water-gen system literally draws clean drinking water out of thin air when children learn about our planet's water cycle, they're taught a simple concept: the atmosphere is filled with water vapor that has evaporated from the bodies of liquid water we see around us. when the vapor's temperature decreases enough, it returns to it's liquid state.
